hearts of Thy servants, and reveal to them Thy great purpose.  May they follow Thy commandments and abide in Thy law.  Help them, O God, in their endeavor, and grant them strength to serve Thee.  O God!  Leave them not to themselves, but guide their steps by the light of Thy knowledge, and cheer their hearts by Thy love.  Verily, Thou art their Helper and their Lord.","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"chr","lang_name":"Cherokee"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"mi","lang_name":"Maori"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"mic","lang_name":"Mikmaq"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"* Short Obligatory Prayer\n\nAs kw'áñsna ta ts'íya wus ha7 szaytn, Olh xa7 lh Kwúkwpi7 lhn skáts'za7, áwi7 ta7s ha7wís tsutsámxw.\nA a7 s-hakstsín as tsutána ta ts'íya wus aslhk'emtayp pilaxentsút kn ts7aylh áwi7 ta támas\ntá7a han szugwzúgwt, ta ts'íya wus ha skwankwánt ta tákmus ha7 szugwzugwt.\n\n Táwi7 ta7 xwúytsu7h-kwúkwpi7 tlu tsukw ha7wi, ta Sknúxwatip, tatá7a sentsukwmina ta7 wa7áx tlu7 tsukw ha7wi.\n\n \n\nI bear witness, O my God, that Thou has created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify at this moment to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\nThere is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-subsisting.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"cr","lang_name":"Cree"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malay